[SN]TITLE[SN]
Livestock auctioneer John Swan and Sons takeover cleared

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A court has sanctioned a takeover bid by Carlisle-based H&H Group of livestock auctioneer John Swan and Sons.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The boards of the two companies had agreed the acquisition in July following protracted talks.
